12:
Looks like this area's all cleaned up
now.
25: W-was that a shift just now?
29:
Yes. Things are getting increasingly
unstable here, just as the Guild said.
31:
The emerging monsters seem to be
increasing in number as well.
34:
...Perhaps it would be best if we
didn't bring you along in the future,
Misogi.
37:
But... If there are more shifts, then
that means we'll have more
chances to find a way back to
Landosol, right?
41:
So I'm gonna do my best to help you
down here!
44:
...You have a point. However,
remember that shifts are extremely
dangerous things. We must exercise
more caution than ever.
54:
Just stick close to us, and you'll be
fine.
78:
Wait!
I think I just heard something...
88: Tch! There's so many of them!
92:
We're getting nowhere! What do we
do?
97:
Hey, guys! I just thought of
something!
106: I've got just the trick for this!
113:
Ha, got 'em! Operation Pitfall was a
resounding success!
120:
I noticed how weak this floor
seemed earlier, and my brain got
right to work hatching a super plan!
123:
If anyone knows how to spot an
opportunity for a prank, it's me!
127: You did a fine job, Misogi—
140: Yes, and it must've been close...
149: Misogi, wait! Don't get any closer!
151:
Who knows what world that shift
might be connected to! If you go
any further, you won't be able to
return!
166:
This is a forest in Landosol I always
play in with my friends!
170:
Really?! Then quick! Jump in so you
can go home!
187:
You idiot! You're gonna miss your
chance!
207:
Never mind! I'm not going home just
yet!
220:
Mm-mmm, so tasty! Food tastes
best right after exploring!
223:
What world are we gonna explore
next? My vote's for going
somewhere we can find some new
pranking materials...
229:
...Misogi. Are you sure it's okay you
didn't go home?
243:
But it was such a rare chance you
passed up on...
250:
...But I couldn't just leave without
Mimi and Kyoka.
254:
It wouldn't be any fun to go home
alone and just wait for everyone to
come back. What a bore!
257:
I want to be together with everyone
else!
261:
...I see. In that case, moving forward,
it would be best if you all searched
together for a way back.
264:
Yeah! I'm gonna work hard to be an
amazing explorer who can help her
friends out of all sorts of trouble!
267: We're all eagerly awaiting that day.
271:
Really?! I've got a lot of traps I
wanna test out, actually...
275:
Heh... Nothing wrong with pranks in
moderation, eh?
278:
Well, it's not like she's gonna land
every prank she tries.
282:
Oh? But Nimbus, I already got you a
while ago. See? Look at your butt...
286:
Hahaha! Gotcha! I didn't do
anything!
293:
Guess we're gonna have to be on
our guard all the time now...
297: Hehe! I'm happy to be with you guys!
